title: [SOLVED]Green light very dark 820-2936-A works only battery macbook pro 2011
message:
1) What does PPBUS_G3H measure without the battery?

2) What voltage do you get on CHGR_ACIN and CHGR_DCIN?

3) What is the resistance between pins 27/28, and pins 17/18 of U7000?

title: [SOLVED]Green light very dark 820-2936-A works only battery macbook pro 2011
message:
Hello
Without Battery :
PPBUS_G3H 12,18V
CHGR_ACIN 3,96V  CHGR_DCIN 16,38
At pins 27/28 24,2 Ohm , Pins 17/18 6,8 Ohm of U7000

title: [SOLVED]Green light very dark 820-2936-A works only battery macbook pro 2011
message: Measure resistance to GND on ACOK line. If that is not really low it is probably a dead 6259.
